Class PSOReverseSlotContentFinder

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.services.assembly.impl.finder.PSBaseSlotContentFinder
      com.percussion.pso.finder.PSOReverseSlotContentFinder
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.percussion.extension.IPSExtension, com.percussion.services.assembly.IPSSlotContentFinder
public class PSOReverseSlotContentFinder
extends com.percussion.services.assembly.impl.finder.PSBaseSlotContentFinder
implements com.percussion.services.assembly.IPSSlotContentFinder

This slot finder returns all of the Active Assembly parents of the current item. The results can be limited by Slot name. The parameters may be supplied in the usual ways: via the slot finder parameters in the slot, or vai the template.

  • max_results limits the total number of items returned in the slot
  • order_by sorts the results by a field (or property). Use ASC and DESC to control direction of the sort.
  • limit_public limits the results to items where the public revision has a relationship to this item. Supply any non-blank value.
  • source_slot limits the results to those items where the current item is in the named slot

Author:
DavidBenua
